8 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to approve the
9 amendments to the charter of the Town of Essex to provide that a Selectboard
10 member’s office shall be deemed vacant if the member removes from the
11 Town or fails to attend at least 50 percent of the meetings of the Selectboard in
12 any calendar year; to establish the duties of the Town Moderator and
13 procedures for the election of a Moderator Pro Tempore in the absence of the
14 Moderator; to authorize the Selectboard to appoint the members of the Town
15 Cemetery Commission; to eliminate certain officers from the list of officers
16 that shall be appointed by the Selectboard; to require the Selectboard to
17 employ a public accountant to examine the financial statements of the funds of
18 the Town; and to correct grammar, references, and style throughout the charter.
